"*name* is the \"short\" library name without any prefix like ``lib``, suffix "
"like ``.so``, ``.dylib`` or version number. (This is the form used for the "
"posix linker option :option:`!-l`.) The result is in a format suitable for "
"passing to :py:class:`~ctypes.CDLL`."
msgstr ""

